class.name: FieldMatrixPreservingVisitor

javadoc.text: Interface defining a visitor for matrix entries.
javadoc.param: <T> * the type of the field elements

javadoc.text:
Start visiting a matrix. *

This method is called once before any entry of the matrix is visited.
javadoc.param: rows number of rows of the matrix
columns number of columns of the matrix
row row index of the entry
column column index of the entry
value current value of the entry

javadoc.text:
End visiting a matrix. *

This method is called once after all entries of the matrix have been visited.
javadoc.return: the value that the walkInXxxOrder must return
